{"tid":557623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次天災人禍都睇到香港人啲劣根性","createTime":"2018-02-11T14:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T14:17:00.000Z","uid":162981,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d21325138bb10f148811ea27cd7a0c6e5648bc9c","tid":557623,"uid":162981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"今次炒車 先唔講話係咪真係關司機情緒累事  但見到連報新聞嘅都可以未審先判已經覺得好譁然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n所有事發經過都未有證據 已經個撚個出曬嚟做判官<br />\n最撚痴線係可以由一開始個個話rip 去到有名單證實大部分係中坑 就轉撚曬呔做抵撚死<br />\n屌 你哋成撚日話台狗蝗戇鳩 但下下死人冧樓 只要唔關自己事都可以鳩噏唔洗本 同狗有乜撚嘢分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚大個人講嘢用下腦啦 唔係冇人知你邊個就唔洗對自己對人負責 係咪少少自制能力都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底香港仲有幾多人叫有返少少人性"},{"pid":"88218fe9b48c315232ea804787b7832413ab8810","tid":557623,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bb993908cd57356909c532f061a38a94f413335","tid":557623,"uid":126681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"上連登勿認真"},{"pid":"040f0423c39b0bcbe16b506951e9446009b8e299","tid":557623,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"最撚有道德係你呀等未？"},{"pid":"21e185e1b8b329fe38c49ec195b2ad390562fd4c","tid":557623,"uid":162981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb993908cd57356909c532f061a38a94f413335","tid":557623,"uid":126681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"上連登勿認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"幾時開始攞鳩噏做擋箭牌 就可以乜柒都唔洗諗"},{"pid":"c7fc6d15f158b4d6a6b7b665f953b37d3cb1babe","tid":557623,"uid":11977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"上網唔9up 等幾時？"},{"pid":"7e01b909680e2964029b9de187d605dbee84d5b3","tid":557623,"uid":162981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,